################################################################################
# MONTHLY VALIDATION CHECKLIST
################################################################################

# Every month, run all 5 queries and:
# [ ] Quality metrics: all datasets >= 0.90 score
# [ ] Policy compliance: 100% of policies marked COMPLIANT
# [ ] Lineage health: all datasets status = HEALTHY
# [ ] Integration contracts: all cross-domain integrations have SLAs
# [ ] Compliance coverage: all domains declare required frameworks
# [ ] Review and update contracts with findings
# [ ] Schedule remediation for any non-compliant items

